snippet.title: Eternal Maze Announcement Trailer (Android)
snippet.description:
Eternal Maze is an upcoming Puzzle Adventure game based on the crop circle phenomenon. Players are to find ways to escape the endless maze by exploring and using whatever they can find in the maze. 

Download now: 
#AppStore: https://goo.gl/PyT5Mb
#GooglePlay: https://goo.gl/eDgdrO
#Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/652990/Eternal_Maze/

For more information please go to:

Facebook Page: https://www.facebook.com/theeternalmaze/
Official Page: http://playplayfun.com/eternal-maze-game-official-page/
